  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6c8c6c4c-7e82-442e-bbab-e77281032e0d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-daef14c2-e83c-420c-aa91-09cdd265cfed\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7917cf80-8166-4a23-8e5a-0a8fd6863893\"><b>안녕하세요 몸과 마음을 건강하게,</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0adfbebb-eb09-4bee-a57c-a3322f083adb\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffef34;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c8ade8a1-eb8e-44f0-83cb-a8884a231d88\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0d7e2812-842b-48e7-8818-0626d7834d68\"><b>입니다!</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-6c8c6c4c-7e82-442e-bbab-e77281032e0d\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3c282f8a-7a81-481c-90b7-9eeee93e49d4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"1\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_1.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-05eb24d1-3c66-411f-8d79-2892f39d963a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dbc27b00-5761-4ea0-848d-93efd6457d1c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-58864294-e50d-4eb4-b27d-cce2aab7751f\"><b>중풍, 어느 날 갑자기 찾아오지 않습니다</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-97a92c12-1341-41c3-8fc6-fd7d8b8a2edd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-a52c0248-68f3-46af-95ee-2e135413f3be\">10명 중 9명이 소양인·태음인 체질?!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c6f1dda5-543f-4faf-b93d-84b3ed02d187\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-dc77c3ae-a1ba-49e7-8f8f-e8e10fb5c0cd\">“중풍은 노인들만 걸리는 병 아니야?”</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7c4e2b4b-8f62-4ae5-80af-94d2d932db35\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-de26ddf3-db08-4107-bf78-5ffe298cb7ac\">“갑자기 쓰러지는 거라 어쩔 수 없지 않나?”</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b4b98ac5-3325-4852-8ddd-b49456d2f154\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-983add68-7fff-4372-8a67-7dac726c8df3\">그렇지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e9ae3b9f-6040-4080-b139-915abb414258\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-52a7c3f7-a65e-421f-bce4-831e7923025f\">중풍(뇌졸중)은 갑자기 일어나는 것처럼 보여도, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b25a8712-e086-4e01-972f-5dd1cbdf4fb7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-3c0d81f1-13aa-44de-afe6-8dacef21c389\">오랜 시간 쌓여온 몸의 경고입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dc151e93-6047-4492-b0c5-e64fe34a4436\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-0dfb55e7-2a6a-4364-af49-b75498d6dd04\">특히 한의학에서는 소양인과 태음인 체질에서 중풍 발병률이 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-46053aff-bb43-4d48-82b2-b8bc1b28189f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-22d06015-3cba-4417-987e-062e358a58d6\">월등히 높다고 보고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1a1d616f-4998-44dc-9003-66ffc0c792ab\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-73f3916b-299f-44ab-9b3b-175995704de9\">실제로 중풍 환자 10명 중 9명 이상이 이 두 체질인 것으로 확인되기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-05eb24d1-3c66-411f-8d79-2892f39d963a\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2ae44eff-fa7e-4279-bc42-0b91f323d8ce\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-2ae44eff-fa7e-4279-bc42-0b91f323d8ce\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/14151faa06d23a02.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1900\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1900\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/14151faa06d23a02.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/14151faa06d23a02.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-2ae44eff-fa7e-4279-bc42-0b91f323d8ce\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0d34d4b2-2a5c-48d9-9c1e-c7c3ac46ad22\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-258da04c-ba9d-4076-9751-505fb1c54b64\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-a20de994-bc00-460c-b9d9-488aa27b34ee\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-0d34d4b2-2a5c-48d9-9c1e-c7c3ac46ad22\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-e67c539a-b318-49c1-88c5-d84079b8693f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-732cc1a4-cff4-4e2b-a3eb-03a59e7d68d7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ee7ead72-cd2a-4f6e-a87b-1652f21c221c\"><b> 왜 소양인과 태음인이 중풍에 취약할까요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a07c5d99-fdfa-40e0-9a48-20562dd2880b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c14447fe-885b-45c1-9476-5daa15892b59\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-07224662-fc87-403a-b4da-f684846a8848\"><b>소양인</b></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b33f0ebf-be2b-4677-b295-846cf7a77997\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-db1d3e3a-558e-434f-8c21-33df4a02eff4\">몸에 열이 많고, 위장 기능은 상대적으로 약한 체질</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4f41455b-192f-4fc1-ad11-a04cc22846cc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-7c5031e5-99f8-4f6f-8b7c-a5dd9b7206e4\">갱년기 이후 심장 두근거림, 불면, 고혈압 증상이 나타나면서 혈관 손상 위험 증가</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e1b4b249-3ddf-4d9f-a36e-872f7a69e1f2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-282988b4-0610-4831-a5a7-b6153509d21f\">성격이 급하고 스트레스를 쉽게 받는 경우도 많아 혈압 변동 폭이 큼</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-846fdd75-71cf-4d8f-a2ef-0b2a8321d34e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-e25e881c-7415-46fe-8c0d-ea8d6976ed76\">​</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b3a03852-a591-464b-ae56-b5867601f943\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4b992f59-0303-4289-b70f-e3af0895a3a3\"><b>태음인</b></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5ed4051f-9d74-4848-9faa-15983f31ce2d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-35be60c7-7cc6-4658-9d4b-46e5a18c74f4\">간 기능은 강하지만 폐 기능이 약한 체질</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b259b044-3bf4-41e6-b3cb-3d7dbe892384\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-6cdafd27-55c9-4e68-b616-e7a29eab7ac7\">잘 먹고 잘 자는 편이지만, 비만과 고혈압으로 이어지기 쉬움</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ecc1a901-6af0-4ec2-a15f-8e376bee49a1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-80295ee8-d8d0-4dd5-9e63-cde36b041f46\">혈관에 부담이 가는 생활습관(과식, 운동 부족 등)이 중풍 위험을 높임</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-a07c5d99-fdfa-40e0-9a48-20562dd2880b\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-c323bca3-fba7-49ee-ade9-be8fac967f27\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-addd7972-3606-48c3-a25f-ff1a6bc20ea8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-da5c5680-5491-434c-a0c7-4e7f7c995e4a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9deeeac6-1eaa-4043-9b68-457eee6edcb1\"><b>체질에 따라 중풍 예방도 달라야 합니다</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-80798677-848b-49f2-99cf-ac68f6e7bfa6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5fc4ce6a-0db9-4798-a1f3-b9b22b7519bb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ebb43453-7650-441a-8986-dd83061ed357\"><b>소양인이라면?</b></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2f3a38a6-9b8a-4a98-82cf-09457965c546\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-a7a3e1fa-e15a-469b-8abe-27d099b2eccd\">열을 내리고 스트레스를 낮추는 식습관이 중요</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4236ca2f-d9ac-4de9-b506-bcfe2d3cb7c6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-385b5058-09c7-4b3a-973a-90a764d097ae\">너무 맵고 자극적인 음식은 피하고, 몸을 차분하게 해주는 한약 복용 권장</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f6d03a33-bfdd-4c96-b5b4-6edd01648095\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-3b43242b-d367-41e1-ae5c-a5cdaee7b5f6\">수면 리듬 유지와 심리 안정이 예방의 핵심</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fb2d5264-c218-420c-b4ff-aeb48c530dc5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-6dab6c5f-d4e7-4465-9457-eac16bffe630\">​</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bafe2b3c-051e-43fd-a6de-025126f4f4e7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2cf5c0a6-b002-4b56-994d-909cab5a2a81\"><b> 태음인이라면?</b></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-908813c1-a699-473b-8e3b-8d0829c89940\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-e651a9bb-793b-47b6-8958-ea9a6d843880\">체중 관리와 꾸준한 유산소 운동 필수</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-67423ff7-88d2-493b-b22a-a6870a793b95\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-d97ba116-e08b-4946-bd50-1174ca3559d4\">기름진 음식, 과식 습관은 반드시 줄이기</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-70b98728-f571-481c-b80c-4cea94fe3085\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-ca9e7477-bdb8-4342-b0d2-ed7a0e083b34\">간 해독과 혈압 관리에 좋은 한약으로 순환을 도와야 중풍을 막을 수 있어요</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-80798677-848b-49f2-99cf-ac68f6e7bfa6\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-80477e6c-d7a3-426f-a85c-7d1e1cfc9236\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-80477e6c-d7a3-426f-a85c-7d1e1cfc9236\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fc0aa489412e10f9.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1536\", \"